---
const wa = "https://wa.me/628159203331?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20mau%20servis%20motor.";
---

<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bengkel Mas Yono — Servis Motor Terpercaya</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; background: #fff; }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

    .nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1.2rem 2rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .nav-logo { font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.3rem; color: #DC2626; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; color: #555; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #DC2626; }
    .nav-cta { background: #DC2626; color: #fff; padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; }

    .hero { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero .badge { display: inline-block; background: rgba(220,38,38,0.2); color: #EF4444; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 50px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #EF4444; }
    .hero p { color: #999; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .hero-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: #DC2626; color: #fff; padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }

    .services { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .services h2 { font-size: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .services-sub { text-align: center; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .srv-card { border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
    .srv-card:hover { border-color: #DC2626; }
    .srv-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; background: #FEE2E2; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .srv-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .srv-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .srv-price { font-weight: 700; color: #DC2626; margin-top: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .about { background: #F9FAFB; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .about-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
    .about-img { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #333, #111); border-radius: 1rem; aspect-ratio: 4/3; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .about h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .about p { color: #666; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .about-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-num { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; color: #DC2626; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #666; }


    .cta-section { background: #DC2626; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-section p { opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: #fff; color: #DC2626; padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; }

    footer { background: #111; color: #666; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    footer a { color: #EF4444; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-logo">🔧 Bengkel Mas Yono</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#layanan">Layanan</a>
      <a href="#tentang">Tentang</a>
      <a href="#lokasi">Lokasi</a>
    </div>
    <a href={wa} class="nav-cta" target="_blank">Hubungi</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="badge">Bengkel Motor Terpercaya</span>
      <h1>Servis motor <span>cepat & jujur</span>, harga pasti.</h1>
      <p>Sudah 12 tahun melayani ribuan pelanggan. Mekanik berpengalaman, suku cadang asli, garansi servis.</p>
      <a href={wa} class="hero-btn" target="_blank">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a9.9 9.9 0 0 0-8.5 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.4A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Z"/></svg>
        Booking Servis
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services" id="layanan">
    <h2>Layanan Kami</h2>
    <p class="services-sub">Servis lengkap untuk semua jenis motor</p>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="srv-card">
        <div class="srv-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" fill="#DC2626" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 18C5.9 18 5 18.9 5 20S5.9 22 7 22 9 21.1 9 20 8.1 18 7 18M17 18C15.9 18 15 18.9 15 20S15.9 22 17 22 19 21.1 19 20 18.1 18 17 18M7.2 14.6L7.1 14.3L8.1 12.5H15.5C16.2 12.5 16.8 12.1 17.1 11.5L21 4.3L19.3 3.5L15.5 10.5H8.5L4.3 2H1V4H3L6.6 11.6L5.2 14.1C4.5 15.2 5.3 16.5 6.5 16.5H19V14.5H7.2Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Servis Rutin</h3>
        <p>Ganti oli, tune-up, cek kelistrikan, dan perawatan berkala lainnya.</p>
        <div class="srv-price">Mulai Rp 75.000</div>
      </div>
      <div class="srv-card">
        <div class="srv-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" fill="#DC2626" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22.7 19L13.6 9.9C14.5 7.6 14 4.9 12.1 3C10.1 1 7.1 0.6 4.7 1.7L9 6L6 9L1.6 4.7C0.4 7.1 0.9 10.1 2.9 12.1C4.8 14 7.5 14.5 9.8 13.6L18.9 22.7C19.3 23.1 19.9 23.1 20.3 22.7L22.6 20.4C23.1 19.9 23.1 19.3 22.7 19Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Overhaul Mesin</h3>
        <p>Bongkar pasang mesin, ganti piston, boring, dan perbaikan berat lainnya.</p>
        <div class="srv-price">Mulai Rp 500.000</div>
      </div>
      <div class="srv-card">
        <div class="srv-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" fill="#DC2626" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12S6.48 22 12 22 22 17.52 22 12 17.52 2 12 2M12 20C7.58 20 4 16.42 4 12C4 10.15 4.63 8.45 5.69 7.1L16.9 18.31C15.55 19.37 13.85 20 12 20M18.31 16.9L7.1 5.69C8.45 4.63 10.15 4 12 4C16.42 4 20 7.58 20 12C20 13.85 19.37 15.55 18.31 16.9Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Ganti Ban & Velg</h3>
        <p>Ban tubeless, ban luar dalam, velg racing. Stok lengkap berbagai merk.</p>
        <div class="srv-price">Mulai Rp 120.000</div>
      </div>
      <div class="srv-card">
        <div class="srv-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" fill="#DC2626" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 3L1 9L5 11.18V17.18L12 21L19 17.18V11.18L21 10.09V17H23V9L12 3M18.82 9L12 12.72L5.18 9L12 5.28L18.82 9M17 15.99L12 18.72L7 15.99V12.27L12 15L17 12.27V15.99Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Kelistrikan</h3>
        <p>Perbaikan starter, pengisian aki, lampu, klakson, dan sistem injeksi.</p>
        <div class="srv-price">Mulai Rp 50.000</div>
      </div>
      <div class="srv-card">
        <div class="srv-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" fill="#DC2626" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.92 6.01C18.72 5.42 18.16 5 17.5 5H6.5C5.84 5 5.28 5.42 5.08 6.01L3 12V20C3 20.55 3.45 21 4 21H5C5.55 21 6 20.55 6 20V19H18V20C18 20.55 18.45 21 19 21H20C20.55 21 21 20.55 21 20V12L18.92 6.01M6.5 16C5.67 16 5 15.33 5 14.5S5.67 13 6.5 13 8 13.67 8 14.5 7.33 16 6.5 16M17.5 16C16.67 16 16 15.33 16 14.5S16.67 13 17.5 13 19 13.67 19 14.5 18.33 16 17.5 16M5 11L6.5 6.5H17.5L19 11H5Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Body & Cat</h3>
        <p>Perbaikan body, pengecatan ulang, pemasangan striping dan aksesoris.</p>
        <div class="srv-price">Mulai Rp 200.000</div>
      </div>
      <div class="srv-card">
        <div class="srv-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" fill="#DC2626" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.63 5.84C17.27 5.33 16.67 5 16 5L5 5.01C3.9 5.01 3 5.9 3 7V17C3 18.1 3.9 18.99 5 18.99L16 19C16.67 19 17.27 18.67 17.63 18.16L22 12L17.63 5.84Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Home Service</h3>
        <p>Motor mogok? Kami datang ke lokasi kamu. Area Jabodetabek.</p>
        <div class="srv-price">Mulai Rp 100.000</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about" id="tentang">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-img">
        <svg width="80" height="80" fill="white" opacity="0.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22.7 19L13.6 9.9C14.5 7.6 14 4.9 12.1 3C10.1 1 7.1 0.6 4.7 1.7L9 6L6 9L1.6 4.7C0.4 7.1 0.9 10.1 2.9 12.1C4.8 14 7.5 14.5 9.8 13.6L18.9 22.7C19.3 23.1 19.9 23.1 20.3 22.7L22.6 20.4C23.1 19.9 23.1 19.3 22.7 19Z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Tentang Bengkel Mas Yono</h2>
        <p>Berdiri sejak 2014, Bengkel Mas Yono sudah melayani ribuan pelanggan dengan prinsip kerja jujur, harga transparan, dan hasil memuaskan.</p>
        <p>Semua mekanik kami bersertifikat dan berpengalaman menangani berbagai merk motor: Honda, Yamaha, Suzuki, Kawasaki, dan lainnya.</p>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">12+</div><div class="stat-label">Tahun Pengalaman</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">5000+</div><div class="stat-label">Motor Diservis</div></div>
          <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">4.8</div><div class="stat-label">Rating Google</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Motor bermasalah? Chat aja dulu.</h2>
    <p>Konsultasi gratis, estimasi harga langsung.</p>
    <a href={wa} class="cta-btn" target="_blank">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#DC2626"><path d="M12 2a9.9 9.9 0 0 0-8.5 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.4A10 10 0 1 0 12 2Zm0 18.1c-1.6 0-3.1-.4-4.4-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.1 8.1 0 1 1 12 20.1Zm4.5-6c-.2-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.5.1-.2.2-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.6 6.6 0 0 1-3.3-2.9c-.2-.4.2-.4.7-1.3 0-.2 0-.3-.1-.4l-.8-1.9c-.2-.5-.4-.4-.5-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.4.1-.7.3-.2.3-.9.9-.9 2.1s.9 2.5 1 2.6c.1.2 1.8 2.7 4.3 3.8.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3Z"/></svg>
      Chat WhatsApp
    </a>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Bengkel Mas Yono. Dibuat oleh <a href="https://webtermajuumkm.com">Websitetermaju</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
